'''夏堅'''<ref name="星島140718"/><ref name="星島141130"/><ref name="星島151021"/> {{post-nominals|country=CAN|PC}} （{{lang|en|Kent Hehr}}，{{bd|1969年|12月16日|||catIdx=Hehr, Kent}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物和律師，[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]]黨員，2015年至2019年擔任[[加拿大國會下議院|加拿大國會下議院]]議員，代表[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]的[[卡加利中選區|卡加利中選區]]，並曾於2015年至2018年間先後在[[賈斯汀·杜魯多内閣|賈斯汀·杜魯多内閣]]中出任聯邦退伍軍人部長、[[加拿大國防部|國防部]]副部長和體育及傷殘人士部長。在此之前，他曾於2008年至2015年間擔任[[亞伯達|亞伯達]][[亞伯達省議會|省議會]]卡加利—水牛選區議員<ref name="CBC141129"/>。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年生活 ===
夏堅生於[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]，在[[卡加利|卡加利]]以東的赫薩爾村（{{lang|en|Hussar}}）長大，七歲時跟家人遷至卡加利<ref name="Macleans160208">{{cite news |url=http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/kent-hehr-the-energizer-bunny-whos-back-in-the-game/ |title=Kent Hehr: The Energizer Bunny who's back in the game |publisher=《[[麥克林|麥克林]]雜誌》 |first=Jason |last=Markusoff |date=2016-02-08 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308115731/http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/kent-hehr-the-energizer-bunny-whos-back-in-the-game/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他父母皆為教育工作者，父親李察曾任卡加利公校教師工會主席，母親茱迪則當選卡加利教育局學務委員<ref name="Macleans160208"/>。夏堅年少時熱衷體育，曾參與少年[[冰球|冰球]]和[[棒球|棒球]]活動，並曾效力亞伯達初級冰球聯盟（{{lang|en|Alberta Junior Hockey League}}）的卡加利加人隊（{{lang|en|Calgary Canucks}}）<ref name="Macleans160208"/>。他後來放棄成為職業冰球員，改為計劃當體育教師並到[[皇家山學院|皇家山學院]]修讀，期間效力該校的冰球隊<ref name="Macleans160208"/>。

1991年10月3日，他跟友人消遣後乘私家車離開，被另一部車輛中兩人開槍擊中頸部，脊柱受損，自此胸部以下癱瘓<ref name="Macleans160208"/><ref name="CBC100917">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/hehr-bares-bullet-ads-1.973336|title=Hehr bares 'bullet' ads|work=CBC News|date=2010-09-17|accessdate=2016-01-13|archive-date=2016-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114234257/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/hehr-bares-bullet-ads-1.973336|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一年後他在父親鼓勵下到[[卡加利大學|卡加利大學]]進修<ref name="Macleans160208"/>，1997年獲得文學士學位後在同校修讀法律<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ucalgary.ca/alumni/archawards/gradofdecade |title=Graduate of the Last Decade |publisher=[[卡加利大學|卡加利大學]] |accessdate=2016-03-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324085516/http://www.ucalgary.ca/alumni/archawards/gradofdecade |archivedate=2017-03-24 }}</ref>。他於2001年獲取法學士學位後加入菲沙、米爾納與卡斯格雷恩律師事務所（{{lang|en|Fraser Milner Casgrain}}），成為該行的民事訴訟律師<ref name="Macleans160208"/><ref name="bio">{{cite web |url=https://khehr.liberal.ca/biography/ |title=Meet Kent Hehr |publisher=[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]] |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318132240/http://khehr.liberal.ca/biography/ |archive-date=2016-03-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

他亦參與社會事務，曾為加拿大聯合公益金（{{lang|en|United Way}}）服務，並曾領導加拿大下身癱瘓者協會的亞伯達分會<ref name="bio"/>。2008年他入選《卡加利先驅報》20名引人注目卡加利人名單<ref name="bio"/>。

=== 晉身省政 ===
夏堅於2006年6月贏取[[亞伯達省議會|省議會]]卡加利—水牛選區的亞伯達自由黨候選人提名<ref name="CBC060620">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/liberals-select-lawyer-as-calgary-buffalo-candidate-1.613598 |title=Liberals select lawyer as Calgary-Buffalo candidate |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2006-06-20 |accessdate=2015-09-03 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924162936/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/liberals-select-lawyer-as-calgary-buffalo-candidate-1.613598 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再於2008年3月省選贏取該議席<ref name="CBC080303">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/conservatives-calgary-fortress-resists-change-1.702381 |title=Conservatives' Calgary fortress resists change |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2008-03-03 |accessdate=2015-09-03 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924164836/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/conservatives-calgary-fortress-resists-change-1.702381 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，首度晉身省議會。他在自由黨[[影子内閣|影子内閣]]中先後擔任司法、財政和教育等範疇的評議員<ref name="bio"/>。

幫派罪案於2008年席捲卡城<ref name=ctv1>{{cite news |url=http://calgary.ctvnews.ca/police-consider-new-ways-to-tackle-gang-problem-1.310924 |title=Police consider new ways to tackle gang problem |publisher=CTV Calgary |date=2008-07-24 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2016-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330012637/http://calgary.ctvnews.ca/police-consider-new-ways-to-tackle-gang-problem-1.310924 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，夏堅遂促請省府增加卡城警局資源，讓當局增聘警員在市中心巡邏<ref name=edj1>{{cite news|url=http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/news/story.html?id=ad4e8ea7-66a7-4c50-afde-d8f88868aaa0 |title=Edmonton Journal |work= |publisher=Edmonton Journal |date=2008-07-24 |accessdate=2008-08-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080830053329/http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/news/story.html?id=ad4e8ea7-66a7-4c50-afde-d8f88868aaa0 |archivedate=2008-08-30 }}</ref>。他又在省議會提出議案，給予警方權力扣查載有未經登記槍械的車輛<ref name=ctv1 />，但在缺乏執政進步保守黨省議員支持下於2009年二讀被否決<ref>Alberta Hansard March 9, 2009, 286</ref>。

當時亞伯達自由黨在省議會内只得八席，夏堅感到自己在該黨的作為有限，因此漸生去意<ref name="Macleans160208"/>。他於2010年競逐卡加利市長選舉，但於選前一個月退選並改為支持最終當選的南施（{{lang|en|Naheed Nenshi}}）<ref>{{Cite news |title=Crowded race for Calgary mayor |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/crowded-race-for-calgary-mayor-1.960205 |publisher=CBC News |date=2010-09-20 |accessdate=2015-09-03 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924161257/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/crowded-race-for-calgary-mayor-1.960205 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年省選前，他一度考慮轉投雷德福（{{lang|en|Alison Redford}}）領導下的執政亞伯達進步保守黨，但最終作罷並以自由黨黨員身份連任省議員<ref name="Macleans160208"/>。自由黨在該屆省選只贏取五席，夏堅遂倡議將該黨和亞伯達新民主黨等左翼省級政黨合併，以抗衡右翼的進步保守黨和野玫瑰黨，但建議不獲自由黨和新民主黨高層接納<ref name="Macleans160208"/><ref>{{Cite news |title=Liberal MLA Kent Hehr calls for merger of the left in bid to defeat Tories |url=http://www.calgaryherald.com/news/liberal+kent+hehr+calls+merger+left+defeat+tories/7675634/story.html |first=Kelly |last=Cryderman |newspaper=《卡加利先驅報》 |date=2012-12-09 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2014-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140524003932/http://www.calgaryherald.com/news/Liberal+Kent+Hehr+calls+merger+left+defeat+Tories/7675634/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 國會議員 ===
夏堅於2014年7月宣佈尋求[[卡加利中選區|卡加利中選區]]國會議員的[[加拿大自由黨|聯邦自由黨]]候選人提名<ref name="星島140718">{{cite news |url=http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2014-07-18/headline1405678457d5145645.html |title=夏堅轉戰聯邦政壇 角逐自由黨卡中選區國會議員提名 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 |author=郭康立 |date=2014-07-18 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905093418/http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2014-07-18/headline1405678457d5145645.html |archive-date=2017-09-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並於同年11月獲得自由黨候選人資格<ref name="星島141130">{{cite news |url=http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2014-11-30/headline1417330876d5347950.html |title=夏堅代表聯邦自由黨 爭卡中選區國會議席 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 |date=2014-11-30 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905093005/http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2014-11-30/headline1417330876d5347950.html |archive-date=2017-09-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="CBC141129">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/kent-hehr-named-federal-liberal-candidate-for-calgary-centre-1.2854798 |title=Kent Hehr named federal Liberal candidate for Calgary-Centre |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2014-11-29 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2015-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119203610/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/kent-hehr-named-federal-liberal-candidate-for-calgary-centre-1.2854798 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[2015年加拿大聯邦大選|2015年聯邦大選]]中，夏堅僅以750票之差險勝尋求連任的[[加拿大保守黨|聯邦保守黨]]候選人[[鍾幗麗|鍾幗麗]]<ref name="Macleans160208"/><ref name="CBC151019">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/calgary-centre-election-results-and-riding-info-1.3275852 |title=Kent Hehr defeats Joan Crockatt in Calgary Centre |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2015-10-19 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184530/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/calgary-centre-election-results-and-riding-info-1.3275852 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="星島151021">{{cite news |url=http://calgary.singtao.ca/132228/2015-10-21/post-%E5%A4%8F%E5%A0%85%E8%B4%8F%E5%8D%A1%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%B8%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD/?variant=zh-hk |title=夏堅贏卡城中選區議席 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 |author=郭康立 |date=2015-10-21 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905094431/http://calgary.singtao.ca/132228/2015-10-21/post-%E5%A4%8F%E5%A0%85%E8%B4%8F%E5%8D%A1%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%B8%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD/?variant=zh-hk |archive-date=2017-09-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，聯同在卡加利天景選區勝出的坎格（{{lang|en|Darshan Kang}}）成為1968年大選以來首批在卡城贏取國會議席的聯邦自由黨候選人<ref name="Macleans160208"/><ref name="CBC151019"/><ref name="星島151105"/>。

自由黨在該屆大選重拾執政權，夏堅於2015年11月獲新任總理[[賈斯汀·杜魯多|賈斯汀·杜魯多]]委任為聯邦退伍軍人部長和[[加拿大國防部|國防部]]副部長，首度晉身[[加拿大內閣|內閣]]<ref name="星島151105">{{cite news |url=http://calgary.singtao.ca/144873/2015-11-05/post-%E6%84%9B%E5%9F%8E%E7%B4%A2%E5%B8%8C%E5%8D%A1%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%8F%E5%A0%85%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8D%E4%BB%BB/?variant=zh-hk |title=愛城索希卡城夏堅獲重任 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 |author=郭康立 |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905100243/http://calgary.singtao.ca/144873/2015-11-05/post-%E6%84%9B%E5%9F%8E%E7%B4%A2%E5%B8%8C%E5%8D%A1%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%8F%E5%A0%85%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8D%E4%BB%BB/?variant=zh-hk |archive-date=2017-09-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="CBC151104">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/m/touch/politics/story/1.3304176 |title=Meet Justin Trudeau's new Liberal cabinet |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2016-03-06 |archive-date=2017-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319022208/http://www.cbc.ca/m/touch/politics/story/1.3304176 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。杜魯多於2017年8月重組內閣，夏堅調任體育及傷殘人士部長<ref name="星島170828">{{cite news |url=http://vancouver.singtao.ca/1326532/2017-08-28/post-%E6%9D%9C%E9%AD%AF%E5%A4%9A%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3-%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%8F%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E4%B8%80%E8%81%B7/?variant=zh-hk |title=杜魯多重組內閣 新增原住民事務部長一職 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加西版 |date=2017-08-28 |accessdate=2017-09-04 |archive-date=2017-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905093713/http://vancouver.singtao.ca/1326532/2017-08-28/post-%E6%9D%9C%E9%AD%AF%E5%A4%9A%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3-%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%8F%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E4%B8%80%E8%81%B7/?variant=zh-hk |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Who's who in Prime Minister Justin Trudeau's cabinet shuffle |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/federal-trudeau-cabinet-shuffle-bios-photos-who-1.4265394 |publisher=CBC News |first=Peter |last=Zimonjic |date=2017-08-28 |accessdate=2017-09-04 |archive-date=2017-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903181706/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/federal-trudeau-cabinet-shuffle-bios-photos-who-1.4265394 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

